The residents of Knysna are urged to evacuate their homes as fires ravage the area. Earlier section of the N2 between Knysna and Plettenberg Bay was closed after a family of three from Rheenendal was killed in the fire.Knysna Hospital had to be evacuated due to the deteriorating blaze. Fire services were battling blazes in Wilderness and Plettenberg Bay. People in the upper part of Knysna were urged to evacuate their homes immediately.